[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0439","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0439.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0254","title":"HP OpenView SNMP 团体字符串信息泄露漏洞","description":"HP OpenView 存在隐藏的 SNMP 团体字符串漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可利用该默认团体字符串访问 SNMP 服务，进而读取或修改 MIB 表中的敏感配置信息，导致信息泄露或设备配置被篡改。受影响的系统包括 HP OpenView 网络管理软件，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0254"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-11-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.633","remediation":"升级 HP OpenView 至 NNM 7.53 或更高版本以修复此已知漏洞；立即修改所有 SNMP 团体字符串，禁止使用默认的 public/private 及已知隐藏字符串；在防火墙上限制仅允许受信任的管理主机访问 UDP 161 端口；如业务不需要 SNMP 功能，建议直接禁用 OpenView 的 SNMP 代理服务以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0254","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-239","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-239/","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0254.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0254","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0254.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0254.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0254.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest-data/blob/c8b30957414aefbd6ba0b766db0d40593ba36fba/references/CVE-1999-0254-2025-03-17-1422","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p4hh-f88r-4p2r/GHSA-p4hh-f88r-4p2r.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest/blob/edcc863fa08f9024b1a3afc6f793747fed5f08ff/references/contrib1-CVE-1999-0254-2025-03-17-1422","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/snmp_default_communities.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0439.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0261","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0261.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0118","title":"IBM AIX 4.3 infod 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.3 系统的 infod 组件存在本地权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过 X display 机制向 infod 服务发送特制请求，利用该漏洞获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.3 版本系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用，成功利用后完全控制系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0118"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.630","remediation":"建议升级到 IBM AIX 4.3.3 及以上受支持版本，或安装对应 APAR 补丁 IX72357。如无需 infod 服务，可执行 `stopsrc -t infod` 停止该服务并通过注释 `/etc/inetd.conf` 中相关行禁用，以消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91158980826979&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19287","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0118","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0118.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7pq8-h83c-wwjc/GHSA-7pq8-h83c-wwjc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6c29fe92-c11f-40b7-bc14-92d730f9e4fc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0261.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0207","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0207.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0088","title":"IRIX 和 AIX automountd 服务远程代码执行漏洞","description":"IRIX 和 AIX 系统中的 automountd（autofsd）服务存在远程命令执行漏洞。攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统的该服务发送特制请求，利用服务对输入参数过滤不严的缺陷，以 root 权限执行任意命令，完全控制受影响主机。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，影响 IRIX 及 AIX 操作系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0088"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.370","remediation":"在 AIX 系统上执行 `stopsrc -g automountd` 禁用自动挂载服务，编辑 `/etc/rc.autofs` 注释自动启动项；在 IRIX 系统上执行 `/etc/init.d/autofs stop` 并删除 rc 链接。同时使用防火墙规则过滤 TCP/UDP 6969 端口，限制对 automountd 服务的网络访问。建议将老旧 IRIX/AIX 系统迁移至受支持版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www-1.ibm.com/services/brs/brspwhub.nsf/advisories/852567CC004F9038852566BF007B6393/%24file/ERS-SVA-E01-1998_004_1.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0207.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0402","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0402.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0215","title":"SGI IRIX 和 OpenLinux routed 守护进程文件追加漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 3/4/5/6 及 OpenLinux 1.0/1.1 系统中运行的 routed 路由守护进程存在文件追加写入漏洞。攻击者可通过向目标系统的 routed 服务发送特制的 traceon 路由跟踪数据包，将任意数据追加到系统文件末尾，包括 /etc/passwd 等关键文件，进而实现权限提升或系统控制。该漏洞利用无需认证，远程即可触发，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0215"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-10-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.790","remediation":"建议禁用 routed 服务并改用静态路由或 gated 替代。如确需运行，升级到 IRIX 6.5.2+ 或 OpenLinux 1.1.2+ 版本，并在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 routed 条目后重启 inetd 服务以立即消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-012.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20805","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0215.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0215","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0215.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0215.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-45w3-m25h-r87g/GHSA-45w3-m25h-r87g.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0215.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--580f5a91-46c0-44d8-8dec-8f18301e9dd8.json","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0402.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0143","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0143.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0053","title":"FreeBSD TCP RST 数据包拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 6.2 的 TCP 协议栈存在 TCP RST 包拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过伪造 TCP RST 数据包向已建立的 TCP 连接发送，导致目标系统上的合法 TCP 连接被异常中断。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，可造成受影响服务的可用性下降，影响范围包括运行 FreeBSD 6.2 的系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0053"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:28.047","remediation":"升级至 FreeBSD 7.0-RELEASE 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 FreeBSD 6.3-STABLE 分支的 tcp_input.c 补丁中修复。若无法升级，可在 pf 防火墙上添加规则限制每秒入站 RST 包数量：`pass in proto tcp flags R/R` 结合 `max-packets 100/sec` 作为临时缓解。同时建议在系统层面启用 syncookies（sysctl net.inet.tcp.syncookies=1）以降低 RST 欺骗影响。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6094"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0143.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0003","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0003.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0002","title":"Linux NFS mountd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NFS mountd 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用后可获取受影响系统的 root 权限。该漏洞主要影响 Linux 系统，包括 RedHat Linux 5.1 及 Caldera OpenLinux Standard 1.2 等版本。CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，建议立即升级至修复版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0002"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-10-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:18.113","remediation":"RedHat Linux 5.1 用户应升级至 RedHat Linux 5.2 或安装对应安全补丁；Caldera OpenLinux Standard 1.2 用户需更新至修复版本；SGI 系统应安装公告 19981006-01-I 提供的补丁。在不影响业务的前提下，可禁用 NFS 服务（/etc/init.d/nfs stop）或使用 tcpwrappers（/etc/hosts.allow）限制对 rpc.mountd 的访问来源，同时通过防火墙仅允许可信 IP 访问 RPC 端口（111/TCP/UDP）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-006.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/121","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19096","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0002.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0002.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0002","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0002.json","https://github.com/demisto/content/blob/710308a4be78e89bc993b4d594b444aeb805b7d8/Packs/IntSight/Integrations/Rapid7ThreatCommand/README.md","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0002.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-222m-mgc9-9mqv/GHSA-222m-mgc9-9mqv.json","https://github.com/MAECProject/python-maec/blob/13e66105c9646156060d0896a4d54970ea358f44/maec/bindings/maec_bundle.py","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/FIRSTdotorg/Vuln4Cast/blob/c93910d268aa5b5d2260adb9b5d92094b2d06daf/YearlyVuln4Cast-V1.ipynb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0003.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0005","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0002","title":"Caldera OpenLinux NFS mountd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NFS 服务中的 mountd 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用后可获得 root 权限，实现完全控制目标系统。该漏洞主要影响 RedHat Linux 5.1、Caldera OpenLinux Standard 1.2 等 Linux 发行版，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0002"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-10-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:18.113","remediation":"立即升级 NFS mountd 相关软件包。Red Hat Linux 用户应升级至 5.2 及以上版本；Caldera OpenLinux 用户应升级至 Standard 1.3 及以上版本。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上封锁 NFS 相关端口（如 TCP/UDP 111、2049），或直接禁用 NFS 服务（`/etc/init.d/nfs stop`）及 rpc.mountd 守护进程。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-006.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/121","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19096"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0562","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0562.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0343","title":"The Palace 客户端远程代码执行漏洞","description":"The Palace 是一款图形化在线聊天软件，其客户端存在远程代码执行漏洞。恶意 Palace 服务器管理员可通过向连接的客户端发送特制的指令数据包，诱使客户端执行任意系统命令或程序。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，受害者仅需连接至受控服务器即可触发。该漏洞影响全部 Palace 客户端版本，可导致客户端被完全控制。目前该软件已停止维护，无官方补丁提供。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0343"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-10-02","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"The Palace 客户端软件已于 2000 年代初停止维护，官方未发布任何安全补丁。建议立即停用该软件，迁移至 Signal、Matrix 等仍在维护的即时通讯方案。如确需继续使用，务必在隔离沙箱环境中运行客户端，仅连接可信服务器，并以最小权限账户执行，避免连接不受控的 Palace 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0343","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0343.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0343","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0343.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0343.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3f4ce19e2c9952be92df5da9390e93383644298b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g4rh-vxc3-fpmr/GHSA-g4rh-vxc3-fpmr.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0343.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82274/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0343.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0562.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0369","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0369.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0186","title":"Sun Solaris SNMP 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统 SNMP 子代理程序存在默认团体字符串（community string）漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 SNMP 协议访问目标系统，利用该默认字符串执行任意命令获取 root 权限，或修改系统关键参数。此漏洞影响 Solaris 操作系统多个版本，攻击门槛低且危害极高，CVSS 评分 10.0，属于严重级别。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0186"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:47.033","remediation":"立即修改 SNMP 默认 community string，将 snmpd.conf 中默认的 \"public\" 改为自定义复杂字符串；升级 Solaris 至包含补丁 105230-xx (Solaris 2.5/2.5.1) 或 105231-xx (Solaris 2.4) 及更高版本；如无需 SNMP 子代理功能，禁用 snmpdx 守护进程；在防火墙层面限制 UDP 161 端口仅对可信管理站开放。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.novell.com/cgi-bin/search/searchtid.cgi?/10080762.htm","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-238/"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0369.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0759","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0759.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0505","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 域用户及管理员账户弱口令漏洞","description":"Windows NT 及 Windows 2000 系统中，域用户或管理员账户使用了过于简单、可被轻易猜测的口令。攻击者可通过暴力破解或字典攻击方式，远程或本地尝试登录目标系统的域控制器或成员服务器，成功后可获取该账户的访问权限，进而可能提升至域管理员权限，控制整个 Windows 域环境。该漏洞影响所有未实施强口令策略的 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 域环境。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0505"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.317","remediation":"在域安全策略中启用密码必须符合复杂性要求并设置最小长度≥8位；通过组策略配置账户锁定阈值（5次无效登录锁定30分钟）；升级至Windows Server 2003以上版本以增强Kerberos认证；立即排查并重置所有域管理员账户的弱密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0505","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0505.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0505.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0505","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0505.json","https://github.com/Azure/Azure-Sentinel/blob/bbd7116272e853f39577ba54522637fe18ed9411/Sample%20Data/Custom/beSECURE_ScanResults_CL.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0505.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/smb_login.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0505.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/smb_guest_account.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83215/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0759.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0760","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0760.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0506","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9111,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10797}}","description":"Windows NT 及 Windows 2000 的域用户或管理员账户存在默认密码为空（null）、空白（blank）或缺失（missing）的安全缺陷。该漏洞源于系统在初始配置时未强制为域账户设置强密码，导致攻击者可在无需任何凭证的情况下直接利用空密码远程或本地登录目标域账户。影响范围涵盖运行 Windows NT 与 Windows 2000 的域控制器及加入域的计算机，危害等级较高（CVSS 7.2）。攻击条件为：目标主机开启了域账户登录且相关账户未配置密码。利用方式简单，攻击者可凭空密码直接进行身份认证，进而获取域用户乃至管理员权限，造成信息泄露、权限提升与进一步横向移动的风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0506"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.433","remediation":"为所有 Windows NT/2000 域用户和管理员帐户设置强密码（至少 8 位，含大小写字母、数字和特殊字符）。通过域安全策略启用密码复杂性要求，开启「密码必须满足复杂性要求」和「密码长度最小值」，并禁用「允许使用空白密码的帐户只允许控制台登录」策略。在本地安全策略中将「帐户: 使用空白密码的本地帐户只允许进行控制台登录」设置为已启用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0506","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c271719fd48dcc28619dc324e441b822d7b4bace/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0506.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0506","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0506.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0506.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/907ae4099f60f85a9473cd7e47129d370c445f83/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p477-22hv-c2xc/GHSA-p477-22hv-c2xc.json","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/xerror/parsing/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/smb_login_as_users.nasl","https://github.com/pentestmonkey/yaptest/blob/9ec017c3bba687c66d94693020c7a0b45e265ae2/metasploit-exploit-suggest.pl","https://github.com/openctibr/threatFeeds/blob/3455d6adfb8ec0cc7fbb444ace396770ca5ca6c0/ExploitableVulnerabilitiesFeed.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0760.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0810","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0810.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0546","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 来宾账户未授权访问漏洞","description":"Windows NT 操作系统默认启用了 Guest（来宾）账户，且该账户通常未设置密码或仅使用弱口令。本地或远程攻击者可通过 Guest 账户以空密码或弱口令登录目标系统，获得有限的系统访问权限，进而通过提权操作获取更高权限甚至完全控制目标系统。此漏洞影响所有 Windows NT 系列版本，属于典型的安全配置缺陷。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0546"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.500","remediation":"建议在 Windows NT 中通过「用户管理器」或 `net user guest /active:no` 命令禁用 Guest 账户；或为 Guest 账户设置复杂密码并移除 Administrators 等特权组成员身份。若业务不需要访客访问，应彻底禁用该账户。同时通过组策略限制本地登录权限作为纵深防御措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0546"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0810.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0147","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0147.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0056","title":"Sun Solaris ping 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SunOS/Solaris 系统中 ping 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地用户通过向 ping 程序提交特制参数可触发缓冲区溢出，从而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SunOS 4.x 及 Solaris 2.x 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。攻击者需拥有本地系统普通用户权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0056"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-09-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:28.453","remediation":"立即安装 Sun 官方提供的对应补丁（如 SunOS 5.x 和 Solaris 2.x 的推荐安全补丁集）。如无法打补丁，可临时移除 ping 程序的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/ping），以消除本地提权风险。建议升级至不受影响的 Solaris 版本或迁移至受支持的 Oracle Solaris 发行版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/174"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0147.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1132","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1132.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0779","title":"HP HP-UX SharedX recserv 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统中的 SharedX recserv 组件存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向运行 recserv 服务的目标系统发送特制请求，导致该服务崩溃或停止响应，造成系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 10.01/10.10/10.20/11.00 等多个版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。目前官方已发布补丁修复此漏洞，建议用户升级至最新版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0779"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-09-03","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议立即安装 HP 针对此漏洞发布的安全补丁（HP-UX 10.01/10.10/10.20/11.00 对应补丁号可查询 HP ITRC 安全公告 HPSBUX9810-086）。如无法打补丁，可在 inetd.conf 中注释掉 recserv 服务行并重启 inetd 以禁用该服务，同时在网络边界防火墙封禁 SharedX 相关端口（177/udp），限制仅受信任主机可访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9810-086","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0779"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1132.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0502","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0502.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0302","title":"Sun Solaris FTP 客户端远程命令执行漏洞","description":"SunOS/Solaris 系统的 FTP 客户端存在命令执行漏洞，恶意 FTP 服务器可通过向客户端返回特制的响应数据包，诱使目标系统执行任意命令。攻击者无需认证即可远程触发该漏洞，完全控制受影响系统的 FTP 客户端进程。该漏洞影响 SunOS/Solaris 系列操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，建议用户及时升级相关补丁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0302"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.490","remediation":"建议升级 SunOS/Solaris 至厂商修复版本（如 Solaris 2.6 补丁 105490-05 及更高），或使用替代 FTP 客户端（如 OpenBSD ftp、lftp）替换默认 /usr/bin/ftp。若无法升级，可在 ftp 客户端环境变量 FTPMODE 设为 passive 降低风险，同时限制出站 FTP 连接至可信服务器，并在网络层面阻止连接恶意外部 FTP 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/176"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0502.toml"}]